The Nijmegen Machine Learning Toolbox (NMLT) is a Matlab toolbox 
that is ideally suited for multivariate pattern analysis of neuroimaging data.
It is being developed at the Intelligent Systems Group at the Institute for 
Computing and Inforamtion Science and at the Donders Centre for Cognitive Neuroimaging (DCCN).

